NAME
    Log::ger::Layout::ConvertCase - Example layout plugin to convert the
    case of message

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.003 of Log::ger::Layout::ConvertCase
    (from Perl distribution Log-ger-Layout-ConvertCase), released on
    2020-03-09.

SYNOPSIS
     use Log::ger::Layout ConvertCase => (
         case => 'upper',
     );
     use Log::ger;

     log_warn "hello, world";

    The final message will be:

     HELLO, WORLD

DESCRIPTION
    This is an example layout plugin, mentioned in the Log::ger tutorial.

CONFIGURATION
  case
    Str. Required. Either "upper" or "lower".

HOMEPAGE
    Please visit the project's homepage at
    <https://metacpan.org/release/Log-ger-Layout-ConvertCase>.

